          intro ‚Ąď h‚Ąď
          exact (admissibleForestContractCanonicalPreimage_retargetExternalLeg_map
            hŌÄ hG‚āĀwf A hA hŌĄV hŌĄStar h‚Ąď).symm
    _ = (G‚āĀ.externalLegs.map (Apre.retargetExternalLeg starPre)).map
