/-- **Track B-forest-final-4b ‚ÄĒ the per-parent remnant map is injective on
forest parents.**  This is the *only* place the genuine-forest branch consumes
the semantic kernel `ForestGraphInsertionUniquenessModel`: identity-uniqueness of
