/-- **Track B-forest-final-5-pre ‚ÄĒ parent three-way partition.**  Every parent
component of `q.1.1` is selected `left`, `right`, or `forest`, so the bare
parent carrier splits as `LeftParents ‚ą™ RightParents ‚ą™ ForestParents`.  This is
the genuine-forest analogue of the mixed-branch two-way partition; the recovery
of `q.1.1.elements` will reassemble these three (Left/Right by the off-carrier
