/-! #### Track B-forest-final-4c ‚ÄĒ free-index transport-compat helpers

The cross-`q` `ForestParents` recovery (below) compares a parent `ő≥` taken from
`q‚āĀ` against a candidate `ő≥'` from `q‚āā` whose remnant agrees.  The membership-free
