      (forestQuotientForestSigmaActualQuotientSubgraph_mem_properDisjoint g r)
  intro ő≥‚āĀ hő≥‚āĀ ő≥‚āā hő≥‚āā hne
  rw [‚Üź AdmissibleSubgraph.elements_def,
    forestQuotientForestSigmaMixedCoverOuterCandidate_elements] at hő≥‚āĀ hő≥‚āā
  rcases Finset.mem_union.mp hő≥‚āĀ with hL1 | hR1
  ¬∑ rcases Finset.mem_union.mp hő≥‚āā with hL2 | hR2
    ¬∑ exact hLIPD hL1 hL2 hne
