/-- Sprint F2i-3o-2d: components of the outer forest whose canonical star does
NOT lie in `őī.vertices`.  Complementary to PromotedComponents (F2i-3o-2b);
later passes will show `A.elements = PromotedComponents ‚äĒ NonPromotedComponents`
as a partition. -/
private noncomputable def forestQuotientForestSigmaForestCoverNonPromotedComponents
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
