`‚Ėł` motive matches the equation `congrArg Sigma.fst hEq` syntactically.
Downstream proofs reduce the projections in-context (`show`/`simp`). -/
private theorem forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_repRight_eqRec_of_eq
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen}
    {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    (congrArg Sigma.fst hEq) ‚Ėł
        (forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ).snd =
      (forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā).snd :=
  Sigma_snd_eqRec_of_eq hEq

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-2: `forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph` is
injective (fixed outer index `A`).  Un-perm step: apply the preimage and use
the `mapPermAdmissibleSubgraphPreimage_mapPerm_eq` round-trip. -/
private theorem forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph_injective
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen) (A : forestOuterProperIndex g)
    {B‚āĀ B‚āā : AdmissibleSubgraph (forestOuterActualQuotientGraph g A)}
    (h : forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph g A B‚āĀ =
      forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph g A B‚āā) :
    B‚āĀ = B‚āā := by
  unfold forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph at h
  have h2 := congrArg
    (mapPermAdmissibleSubgraphPreimage (forestOuterActualToRepPerm_spec g A)) h
  rwa [mapPermAdmissibleSubgraphPreimage_mapPerm_eq,
    mapPermAdmissibleSubgraphPreimage_mapPerm_eq] at h2

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-2: generic un-perm under index transport.  For a
*free* outer-index equality `hA : A‚āĀ = A‚āā` (so `cases hA` closes), the
`eqRec`-transported equality of `toRep`-images descends to an `eqRec`-equality
of the underlying actual-quotient forests.  Specialized later to the computed
`MixedOuterIndex` equality. -/
private theorem forestOuterActualToRep_eqRec_inj
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen) {A‚āĀ A‚āā : forestOuterProperIndex g} (hA : A‚āĀ = A‚āā)
    {B‚āĀ : AdmissibleSubgraph (forestOuterActualQuotientGraph g A‚āĀ)}
    {B‚āā : AdmissibleSubgraph (forestOuterActualQuotientGraph g A‚āā)}
    (h : hA ‚Ėł forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph g A‚āĀ B‚āĀ =
      forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph g A‚āā B‚āā) :
    hA ‚Ėł B‚āĀ = B‚āā := by
  cases hA
  exact forestOuterActualToRepAdmissibleSubgraph_injective g A‚āĀ h

/-- **Track B-forest-final-3 ‚ÄĒ genuine-forest quotient equality descends to the
actual quotient forest.**  The genuine-forest `toQuotient` image is
`‚ü®OuterIndex, toRep ActualQuotient‚ü©`; an equality of images gives an outer-index
equality (`fst`) and an `eqRec`-transported equality of `toRep ActualQuotient`
(`Sigma_snd_eqRec_of_eq`); un-`mapPerm` (`forestOuterActualToRep_eqRec_inj`) then
descends it to the underlying actual quotient forest.  This is the genuine-forest
analogue of the mixed-branch un-perm step, with the *actual* quotient forest
(carrying the star-collapsed remnants) recovered before the semantic
insertion-uniqueness kernel is invoked. -/
private theorem forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma_actualQuotient_eqRec_of_eq
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen} {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hOuter :
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āā hq‚āā)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    hOuter ‚Ėł
        forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientSubgraphCanonical g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientSubgraphCanonical g q‚āā hq‚āā :=
  forestOuterActualToRep_eqRec_inj g hOuter
    (Sigma_snd_eqRec_of_eq hEq)

/-- Generic `eqRec`/`elements` congruence over a **free** outer-index equality:
`cases hA` collapses the transport (legal because `A‚āĀ A‚āā` are free variables),
then `.elements` is a plain `congrArg`.  This is the wall-free replacement for a
direct `cases` on a *computed* outer equality (`cases` on
`OuterIndex q‚āĀ = OuterIndex q‚āā` fails dependent elimination ‚ÄĒ the computed-fst
wall). -/
private theorem admissibleSubgraph_elements_eqRec_of_eq
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen) {A‚āĀ A‚āā : forestOuterProperIndex g} (hA : A‚āĀ = A‚āā)
    {B‚āĀ : AdmissibleSubgraph (forestOuterActualQuotientGraph g A‚āĀ)}
    {B‚āā : AdmissibleSubgraph (forestOuterActualQuotientGraph g A‚āā)}
    (h : hA ‚Ėł B‚āĀ = B‚āā) :
    hA ‚Ėł B‚āĀ.elements = B‚āā.elements := by
  cases hA
  exact congrArg AdmissibleSubgraph.elements h

private theorem
    forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientComponents_eq_of_eqRec
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen) {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hOuter :
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āā hq‚āā)
    (h :
      hOuter ‚Ėł
          forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientSubgraphCanonical g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
        forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientSubgraphCanonical g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    hOuter ‚Ėł forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientComponents g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientComponents g q‚āā hq‚āā :=
  admissibleSubgraph_elements_eqRec_of_eq g hOuter h

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-3: data-preserving injectivity of
`admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph` on subgraphs **vertex-disjoint from the
carrier** `A`.  Unlike the star-collapse injectivity (B-1b-2), here retarget
preserves all data (`toFeynmanGraph_eq_of_not_mem`), so equal retargets force
equal sources via `FeynmanSubgraph.ext`.  This is the relevant case for the
mixed-branch RightSubgraph (its components are disjoint from the LeftSubgraph
carrier). -/
private theorem admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph_inj_of_not_mem
    {G : FeynmanGraph} [DivergenceMeasure G]
    (A : AdmissibleSubgraph G) (starOf : FeynmanSubgraph G ‚Üí VertexId)
    {ő≥‚āĀ ő≥‚āā : FeynmanSubgraph G}
    (hE‚āĀ : ő≥‚āĀ.internalEdges ‚Č§ A.complementEdges)
    (hE‚āā : ő≥‚āā.internalEdges ‚Č§ A.complementEdges)
    (hV‚āĀ : ‚ąÄ v ‚ąą ő≥‚āĀ.vertices, v ‚ąČ A.vertices)
    (hV‚āā : ‚ąÄ v ‚ąą ő≥‚āā.vertices, v ‚ąČ A.vertices)
    (h : admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A starOf ő≥‚āĀ hE‚āĀ =
      admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A starOf ő≥‚āā hE‚āā) :
    ő≥‚āĀ = ő≥‚āā := by
  have h1 : ő≥‚āĀ.toFeynmanGraph = ő≥‚āā.toFeynmanGraph := by
    have hc := congrArg FeynmanSubgraph.toFeynmanGraph h
    rwa [admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph_toFeynmanGraph_eq_of_not_mem A starOf ő≥‚āĀ hE‚āĀ hV‚āĀ,
      admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph_toFeynmanGraph_eq_of_not_mem A starOf ő≥‚āā hE‚āā hV‚āā] at hc
  exact FeynmanSubgraph.ext_iff.mpr
    ‚ü®congrArg FeynmanGraph.vertices h1,
     congrArg FeynmanGraph.internalEdges h1,
     congrArg FeynmanGraph.externalLegs h1‚ü©

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-4: from an `eqRec`-equality of certificate-built
actual retargeted forests (free outer index), recover the underlying source
forest element-set equality.  `cases hA` collapses the transport (free index),
then a `Finset.ext` uses the off-carrier retarget injectivity (B-HEq-3) on both
directions.  `hV‚āĀ`/`hV‚āā` supply the vertex-disjointness of the source elements
from the carrier. -/
private theorem forestOuterActualRetargetOfCert_elements_eq_of_eqRec
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen) {A‚āĀ A‚āā : forestOuterProperIndex g} (hA : A‚āĀ = A‚āā)
    {S‚āĀ S‚āā : AdmissibleSubgraph (repG g).toFeynmanGraph}
    (C‚āĀ : forestOuterActualRetargetCertificate g A‚āĀ S‚āĀ)
    (C‚āā : forestOuterActualRetargetCertificate g A‚āā S‚āā)
    (hV‚āĀ : ‚ąÄ ő≥ ‚ąą S‚āĀ.elements, ‚ąÄ v ‚ąą ő≥.vertices, v ‚ąČ A‚āĀ.1.vertices)
    (hV‚āā : ‚ąÄ ő≥ ‚ąą S‚āā.elements, ‚ąÄ v ‚ąą ő≥.vertices, v ‚ąČ A‚āā.1.vertices)
    (h : hA ‚Ėł forestOuterActualRetargetAdmissibleSubgraphOfCert g A‚āĀ S‚āĀ C‚āĀ =
      forestOuterActualRetargetAdmissibleSubgraphOfCert g A‚āā S‚āā C‚āā) :
    S‚āĀ.elements = S‚āā.elements := by
  cases hA
  change forestOuterActualRetargetAdmissibleSubgraphOfCert g A‚āĀ S‚āĀ C‚āĀ =
    forestOuterActualRetargetAdmissibleSubgraphOfCert g A‚āĀ S‚āā C‚āā at h
  -- `.elements` of OfCert reduces to the retarget image by `rfl`; coerce.
  have he :
      S‚āĀ.elements.attach.image (fun ő≥ =>
        admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
          (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
            (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) ő≥.1 (C‚āĀ.edge_le ő≥.1 ő≥.2)) =
      S‚āā.elements.attach.image (fun ő≥ =>
        admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
          (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
            (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) ő≥.1 (C‚āā.edge_le ő≥.1 ő≥.2)) :=
    congrArg AdmissibleSubgraph.elements h
  apply Finset.ext
  intro x
  constructor
  ¬∑ intro hx
    have hxim :
        admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
          (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
            (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) x (C‚āĀ.edge_le x hx) ‚ąą
        S‚āĀ.elements.attach.image (fun ő≥ =>
          admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
            (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
              (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) ő≥.1 (C‚āĀ.edge_le ő≥.1 ő≥.2)) :=
      Finset.mem_image.mpr ‚ü®‚ü®x, hx‚ü©, Finset.mem_attach _ _, rfl‚ü©
    rw [he] at hxim
    obtain ‚ü®‚ü®y, hy‚ü©, _, hxy‚ü© := Finset.mem_image.mp hxim
    have hyx : y = x :=
      admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph_inj_of_not_mem A‚āĀ.1 _
        (C‚āā.edge_le y hy) (C‚āĀ.edge_le x hx) (hV‚āā y hy) (hV‚āĀ x hx) hxy
    rwa [hyx] at hy
  ¬∑ intro hx
    have hxim :
        admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
          (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
            (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) x (C‚āā.edge_le x hx) ‚ąą
        S‚āā.elements.attach.image (fun ő≥ =>
          admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph A‚āĀ.1
            (FeynmanGraph.admissibleForestCanonicalStarOf
              (repG g).toFeynmanGraph A‚āĀ.1 A‚āĀ.2) ő≥.1 (C‚āā.edge_le ő≥.1 ő≥.2)) :=
      Finset.mem_image.mpr ‚ü®‚ü®x, hx‚ü©, Finset.mem_attach _ _, rfl‚ü©
    rw [‚Üź he] at hxim
    obtain ‚ü®‚ü®y, hy‚ü©, _, hxy‚ü© := Finset.mem_image.mp hxim
    have hyx : y = x :=
      admissibleSubgraphRetargetSubgraph_inj_of_not_mem A‚āĀ.1 _
        (C‚āĀ.edge_le y hy) (C‚āā.edge_le x hx) (hV‚āĀ y hy) (hV‚āā x hx) hxy
    rwa [hyx] at hy

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-1a: mixed `toQuotient` equality gives `LeftSubgraph`
equality at the underlying-AdmissibleSubgraph level.  Take `Sigma.fst` of the
target Sigma equality, then unfold `MixedOuterIndex.val` (the simp lemma) to
expose the LeftSubgraph. -/
private theorem forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_leftSubgraph_eq_of_eq
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen}
    {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2 =
      forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph q‚āā.1.1 q‚āā.2 := by
  have hOuter : forestComponentMixedBoundaryOuterIndex g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryOuterIndex g q‚āā hq‚āā :=
    congrArg Sigma.fst hEq
  have hVal := congrArg Subtype.val hOuter
  simpa [forestComponentMixedBoundaryOuterIndex_val] using hVal

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-5a: mixed-branch Left/Right partition of the outer
admissible elements.  In the mixed-boundary regime every component is left or
right (no forest choice), so `Left.elements ‚ą™ Right.elements = A.elements`.
(Local copy preceding the q.1-recovery proof; an identical lemma exists
downstream for the original cover-side caller.) -/
private theorem forestComponentMixedBoundary_left_union_right_elements_recovery
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen}
    (q : forestComponentChoiceSigma g)
    (hq : q ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g) :
    (forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph q.1.1 q.2).elements ‚ą™
        (forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph q.1.1 q.2).elements =
      q.1.1.elements := by
  classical
  have hp : q.2 ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceCoreIndex q.1.1 :=
    (Finset.mem_sigma.mp hq).2
  have hNoForest : ¬¨ forestComponentChoiceHasForest q.1.1 q.2 := by
    unfold forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceCoreIndex at hp
    exact (Finset.mem_filter.mp hp).2
  ext ő≥
  constructor
  ¬∑ intro hő≥
    rcases Finset.mem_union.mp hő≥ with hő≥L | hő≥R
    ¬∑ exact forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph_elements_subset q.1.1 q.2 hő≥L
    ¬∑ exact forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph_elements_subset q.1.1 q.2 hő≥R
  ¬∑ intro hő≥A
    rcases forestCoproductChoice_eq_left_or_right_or_forest
        (ő≥.toHopfGen (q.1.1.isConnectedDivergent_of_mem hő≥A))
        (q.2 ‚ü®ő≥, hő≥A‚ü© (Finset.mem_attach q.1.1.elements ‚ü®ő≥, hő≥A‚ü©)) with
      hLeft | hRightOrForest
    ¬∑ apply Finset.mem_union_left
      rw [forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph_elements]
      exact Finset.mem_filter.mpr ‚ü®hő≥A, by
        unfold forestComponentChoiceIsLeft
        rw [dif_pos hő≥A]; exact hLeft‚ü©
    ¬∑ rcases hRightOrForest with hRight | hForest
      ¬∑ apply Finset.mem_union_right
        rw [forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph_elements]
        exact Finset.mem_filter.mpr ‚ü®hő≥A, by
          unfold forestComponentChoiceIsRight
          rw [dif_pos hő≥A]; exact hRight‚ü©
      ¬∑ rcases hForest with ‚ü®B, hB‚ü©
        exact False.elim (hNoForest ‚ü®‚ü®ő≥, hő≥A‚ü©, B, hB‚ü©)

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-5b: **mixed `q.1` recovery**.  From `toQuotient`
equality, recover the outer proper-index value `q‚āĀ.1 = q‚āā.1`.  Chain:
LeftSubgraph eq (B-1a) + RightSubgraph elements eq (B-HEq-1 ‚Üí un-perm B-HEq-2
‚Üí un-retarget B-HEq-4) + Left/Right partition (B-HEq-5a) gives `A.elements`
equality, closed by `forestOuterProperIndex_eq_of_elements_eq`. -/
private theorem forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_q1_recovery
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen}
    {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    q‚āĀ.1 = q‚āā.1 := by
  -- LeftSubgraph equality (B-1a)
  have hLeft := forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_leftSubgraph_eq_of_eq
    hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hEq
  -- off-carrier vertex-disjointness for Right components
  have hPD‚āĀ : q‚āĀ.1.1.IsPairwiseDisjoint :=
    (repG g).toFeynmanGraph.properDisjointAdmissibleDivergentSubgraphs_isPairwiseDisjoint q‚āĀ.1.2
  have hPD‚āā : q‚āā.1.1.IsPairwiseDisjoint :=
    (repG g).toFeynmanGraph.properDisjointAdmissibleDivergentSubgraphs_isPairwiseDisjoint q‚āā.1.2
  -- RightSubgraph elements equality: un-perm (B-HEq-2) then un-retarget (B-HEq-4)
  have hRight :
      (forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2).elements =
      (forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph q‚āā.1.1 q‚āā.2).elements :=
    forestOuterActualRetargetOfCert_elements_eq_of_eqRec g (congrArg Sigma.fst hEq)
      (forestComponentMixedBoundaryRightRetargetCertificateCanonical g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ)
      (forestComponentMixedBoundaryRightRetargetCertificateCanonical g q‚āā hq‚āā)
      (fun ő≥ hő≥ v hv =>
        forestComponentChoiceRight_vertices_not_mem_leftSubgraph q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2 hPD‚āĀ hő≥ hv)
      (fun ő≥ hő≥ v hv =>
        forestComponentChoiceRight_vertices_not_mem_leftSubgraph q‚āā.1.1 q‚āā.2 hPD‚āā hő≥ hv)
      (forestOuterActualToRep_eqRec_inj g (congrArg Sigma.fst hEq)
        (forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_repRight_eqRec_of_eq hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hEq))
  -- combine via partition
  apply forestOuterProperIndex_eq_of_elements_eq
  rw [‚Üź forestComponentMixedBoundary_left_union_right_elements_recovery q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ,
      ‚Üź forestComponentMixedBoundary_left_union_right_elements_recovery q‚āā hq‚āā,
      hRight]
  rw [show (forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2).elements =
        (forestComponentChoiceLeftSubgraph q‚āā.1.1 q‚āā.2).elements from
      congrArg AdmissibleSubgraph.elements hLeft]

/-- Sprint F2-Track-B-HEq-6: **mixed-branch same-branch injectivity** (the
`mixed_inj` field of `BranchInjectivitySeparation`).  Combines the `q.1`
recovery (B-HEq-5b) with the q.1-fixed injectivity `_inj_of_q1_eq` (F1r-2b). -/
private theorem forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_inj
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen}
    {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentMixedBoundaryChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    q‚āĀ = q‚āā :=
  forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_inj_of_q1_eq hq‚āĀ hq‚āā
    (forestComponentMixedBoundaryToQuotientForestSigma_q1_recovery hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hEq)
    (congrArg Sigma.fst hEq)

/-- **Track B-forest-final-5a ‚ÄĒ RightParents equality.**  From a genuine-forest
`toQuotient` equality, the right-selected parent carriers agree.  Chain: outer
equality (`fst`) ‚Üí actual-quotient `eqRec` (final-3) ‚Üí component-carrier `eqRec`
‚Üí `ActualRight` `eqRec` (raw star-touch separation) ‚Üí off-carrier un-retarget
(`forestOuterActualRetargetOfCert_elements_eq_of_eqRec`, the same data-preserving
route as the mixed branch).  No model, no `cases` on the computed outer
equality. -/
private theorem forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma_rightParents_eq_of_eq
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    {g : HopfGen} {q‚āĀ q‚āā : forestComponentChoiceSigma g}
    (hq‚āĀ : q‚āĀ ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hq‚āā : q‚āā ‚ąą forestComponentForestChoiceSigmaIndex g)
    (hEq :
      forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma g q‚āā hq‚āā) :
    (forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2).elements =
      (forestComponentChoiceRightSubgraph q‚āā.1.1 q‚āā.2).elements := by
  classical
  have hOuter :
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ =
      forestComponentForestChoiceOuterIndex g q‚āā hq‚āā := congrArg Sigma.fst hEq
  have hActual :=
    forestComponentForestChoiceToQuotientForestSigma_actualQuotient_eqRec_of_eq
      hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hEq
  have hComp :=
    forestComponentForestChoiceActualQuotientComponents_eq_of_eqRec
      g hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hActual
  have hActualRight :=
    forestComponentForestChoiceActualRight_eqRec_of_components_eqRec
      g hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hComp
  have hPD‚āĀ : q‚āĀ.1.1.IsPairwiseDisjoint :=
    (repG g).toFeynmanGraph.properDisjointAdmissibleDivergentSubgraphs_isPairwiseDisjoint
      q‚āĀ.1.2
  have hPD‚āā : q‚āā.1.1.IsPairwiseDisjoint :=
    (repG g).toFeynmanGraph.properDisjointAdmissibleDivergentSubgraphs_isPairwiseDisjoint
      q‚āā.1.2
  exact forestOuterActualRetargetOfCert_elements_eq_of_eqRec g hOuter
    (forestComponentForestChoiceRightRetargetCertificateCanonical g q‚āĀ hq‚āĀ)
    (forestComponentForestChoiceRightRetargetCertificateCanonical g q‚āā hq‚āā)
    (fun ő≥ hő≥ v hv =>
      forestComponentChoiceRight_vertices_not_mem_forestOuterSubgraph
        q‚āĀ.1.1 q‚āĀ.2 hPD‚āĀ hő≥ hv)
    (fun ő≥ hő≥ v hv =>
