      g hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hActual
  have hRem :=
    forestComponentForestChoiceRemnantComponents_eq_of_components_eqRec
      g hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hComp
  exact forestComponentForestChoiceForestParents_eq_of_remnant_eqRec
    g hq‚āĀ hq‚āā hOuter hRem

/-- **Track B-forest-final-5b ‚ÄĒ LeftParents equality.**  From a genuine-forest
`toQuotient` equality, the left-selected parent carriers agree.  Plain (no
transport): the outer subgraph carriers agree (`fst`), the forest parents agree
(4c), and `Left = OuterSubgraph \ inside-forest` (helper); rewriting both. -/
