/-- **Track B-forest-final-6 ‚ÄĒ fixed-`q.1` injectivity.**  With the outer index
recovered (`q‚āĀ.1 = q‚āā.1`), the outer-subgraph equality (`fst`) pins the entire
choice function `p` ‚ÄĒ including the genuine-forest `B` payloads ‚ÄĒ via the
