  ¬∑ exact forestComponentForestChoiceSplitStarOf_right_fresh g q hq C hő≥R
  ¬∑ rcases hő≥F with ‚ü®B, hB‚ü©
    exact forestComponentForestChoiceSplitStarOf_forest_fresh
      g q hq C ‚ü®ő≥, hő≥‚ü© hB

