                  exact AdmissibleSubgraph.mem_vertices.mpr ‚ü®ő≥, hő≥R, hvő≥‚ü©)
            exact False.elim (hvNotAct hvAct)
          ¬∑ rcases hő≥F with ‚ü®B, hB‚ü©
