    rcases admissibleForestContractFreshStarFieldRelabeling_of_wellFormed
        (repG_wellFormed g) q.1.1 q.1.2 starOf hFresh with
      ‚ü®ŌĄ, hV, hI, hE‚ü©
    have hOrig :
